      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Age of The Mediathon</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Catherine Doyle letter on Frank Rich's Oct 29 article on Mediathon journalism</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I was perplexed as to why the Clarence Thomas-Anita Hill episode was not included in your Mediathon. Certainly the circus surrounding Thomas's confirmation hearings warrants inclusion. Americans were glued to their televisions with visions of pornography, Senate interrogations and pubic hairs.</p>
        <p>Catherine Doyle  Cambridge, Mass.</p>
      </block>
